{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aa529ded59","title":"昆明工学院右派的反动言论 （3）","origin":"《云南省高等学校右派分子反动言论选集》(中国共产党云南省高等学校委员会办公室编印，1957.8.15)，内部资料。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d48a2682b2","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"aa529ded59"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"a7ea3bd8ce","name":"朱德","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"518e4a772a","name":"苏福寿"},{"id":"59c5d22bf1","name":"凌荣钲"},{"id":"722102ffad","name":"昆明工学院学生"},{"id":"8a2c77c67b","name":"江天龙"},{"id":"caca0997a3","name":"王原强"},{"id":"d546736a88","name":"吕瑾华"},{"id":"e96bcabbd7","name":"张存金"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"67316ba7f8","type":"title","text":"昆明工学院右派的反动言论 （3）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"f1806f26b8","type":"authors","text":"昆明工学院学生凌荣钲苏福寿王富强张存金江天龙吕瑾华","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"36b9135582","type":"paragraph","text":"凌荣钲(昆明工学院采矿系学生)说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"94c00b5483","type":"subtitle","text":"地主阶级有进步性","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"c31b56c0f8","type":"paragraph","text":"地主阶级在近几十年来有进步性，理由是有了地主阶级在农村中占有土地，才保持中国成为半封建半殖民地社会，如没有地主阶级中国早变成殖民地了。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"2a18f3ff44","type":"paragraph","text":"不应该土改，特别是土改中不应该没收地主的全部生产资料，至少应留给他一半。地主交出契约后应与起义将领同样看待。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"30d9675f58","type":"paragraph","text":"苏福寿(昆明工学院冶金系学生)的文章：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"aaa69469fb","type":"subtitle","text":"政治课不应该考试也不应该考查","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"32dddb8dc5","type":"subtitle","text":"二年级无名者","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"a3df538646","type":"paragraph","text":"声明在前：马列主义在中国传播，我是同意的，并且希望传播得更深更广，共产党的领导，我是积极拥护的。现在我提意见主要是为了解决问题，实际减轻同学过重负担，但是我的意见可能会引起一些人——教条主义者的不同意看法，给我安上一些不合适的帽子；我的意见极不是这样。请不要来这一套。下面为我个人不考试也不考查的几点原因：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"c0c16d7938","type":"paragraph","text":"1、我怀疑毛主席说的“马列主义不强加于别人，而是自觉自愿的学习”这话，可能是为了对资本主义国家说得好听一些，加点颜色吧！在国内实际上并没有这样作，考试考查是强迫别人学习的。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"bd41f44e63","type":"paragraph","text":"2、学习内并非全部是党团员，若是，那就应该进行考试。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"769eac70ac","type":"paragraph","text":"3、政治学得好否，并不能从分数高低来看，试问政治得五分，实际表现特别坏（党团员及同学）如何解释？","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"c2f42c3be9","type":"paragraph","text":"4、通过考试不能真实提高同学政治水平，同时加重同学负担，影响其他课程的考试，试问从何提高学习质量？","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"5c475976b1","type":"appellation","text":"要求：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"f4c3d948a3","type":"paragraph","text":"1、需慎重考虑，急速答复。（反对教条式的布告）","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"5ab38e5d78","type":"paragraph","text":"2、要求给予提意见者安全保护。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"9e0c84c4c3","type":"paragraph","text":"建议：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"669c3c4b73","type":"paragraph","text":"1、若学校不能解决，请用电报请示高教部。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"4b0b84a185","type":"paragraph","text":"2、若一定要考，对非党团员者，可以申请不考。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"671c4f4e8d","type":"paragraph","text":"（录自工学院院刊）","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"b4fec2fb0c","type":"paragraph","text":"王富强(昆明工学院采矿系学生、团员)说：","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"d18141514e","type":"subtitle","text":"毛主席搞一个党朱德搞一个党就是两党制","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"3573919e35","type":"paragraph","text":"两党制中国也可以，毛主席搞一个党，朱德搞一个党就是两党制。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"67d83b6301","type":"subtitle","text":"走第三条路线，外交政策两边倒","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"d75aa3687c","type":"paragraph","text":"让章伯钧他们执政，中国也不会走半殖民地半封建的道路，可以走第三条路线。现在国际第三种力量（民族主义国家）还很强大，中国能这样，他们响往资本主义，拿给他们执政走民族主义道路还是好。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"5b70b29a1d","type":"paragraph","text":"他们（第三条路线）能取得苏联和美国的援助，也可以向美国和苏联派留学生，中国如能派留学生到美国还是好，这就是两边倒的外交政策的好处。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"893d066f3a","type":"paragraph","text":"中国到联合国，反正投苏联的票，一票没多大作用，大家都看印度的票，投到那边就起很大作用。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"ed1de56cc6","type":"subtitle","text":"争鸣没有立场问题，用立场分析就是压服","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"05c325618a","type":"paragraph","text":"“争鸣”只有正确与否，没有立场问题，用阶级立场分析是压服。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"249a86d90c","type":"paragraph","text":"说美国出兵朝鲜是侵略，说苏联出兵匈牙利也是侵略，这是什么立场？","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"aced83f826","type":"paragraph","text":"不管立场，只重事实。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"1cda5fcfe8","type":"paragraph","text":"阶级斗争的影响在我幼小的心灵中留下不可磨灭的印象。一方面有党的教育，是共青团员；另一方面思想上的这些创伤又医不了，这是最大的矛盾，很痛心，很伤心。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"5bd173e2dc","type":"subtitle","text":"党管得太宽了","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"b71d8cb7f6","type":"paragraph","text":"党管理太宽了，留学生的家庭总是工人，爱吃爱喝穿花衣服也要管，出版书籍有限制，黄色小说剑侠小说不准看，只准看卓娅与舒拉的故事。班上强调集体，没有自由。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"d9e5dc53da","type":"paragraph","text":"只准信马列主义，不准信唯心主义。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"45408dcc1b","type":"paragraph","text":"优秀文艺作品很少，优秀面很少，艺术落后了，什么都强调工农兵。管得太恼火了。当前文艺理论水平低就是教条主义限制过死的结果。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"89b3c071a0","type":"paragraph","text":"统购统销管得太死了，过去买东西很自由，现在说增产了，买东西还要排队。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"f6dfc3a425","type":"paragraph","text":"吃不到米、肉，经常吃什么粮，吃不饱。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"3d841e54ca","type":"paragraph","text":"买公债也是摊派，上面说自愿，下面不自愿，有名无实。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"1138e4a482","type":"subtitle","text":"不为工人阶级服务也要为工人阶级服务","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"1890fda642","type":"paragraph","text":"政治是强加于人，不管你信不信都要学马列主义，不为工人阶级服务也要为工人阶级服务。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"fc64449cf8","type":"paragraph","text":"主张为国家服务，为人民服务，不同意为工农兵服务。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"d34607085a","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党只能说好，不能说坏，不然就是反动思想，要多喊几个万岁，多说点好听话。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"ed14fac505","type":"subtitle","text":"社会主义制度加官僚主义比资产主义更坏","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"4884fed5c9","type":"paragraph","text":"在我们社会里个性得不到发展，这是西欧民主自由多。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"f826e4f6ba","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义制度加上官僚主义比资本主义更坏，如公私合营前生产高，合营后生产力低了。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"47303e6ab9","type":"paragraph","text":"资本家接受改造是被剥夺得无力反抗只好接受改造。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"27f86bd466","type":"paragraph","text":"农民只口头上拥护党，心理不服，会引起革命。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"5f869a9f5e","type":"subtitle","text":"发点牢骚有人权自由","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"e22611b3dc","type":"paragraph","text":"右派没有什么问题，只是发点牢骚，为什么要拿来整？右派只是少数政客争夺主席总理的职位问题，与广大群众无甚关系，学生中有啥右派分子？","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"652d1861ff","type":"paragraph","text":"反右派斗争是一放二收三整，是诱敌深入，放长线钓大鱼，事实上是整了，还有什么言论自由？","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"e1f3a76092","type":"paragraph","text":"那么多人提问题要一个人答，怎么答得上？要是我就不高兴参加会议，不检讨，你说什么立场就什么立场，为什么鸣只是个人搞没有组织，而反右派斗争要那么大规模的组织，党团动员组织起来整？","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"a5383a8b90","type":"paragraph","text":"要遭整，我也不怕，我没有政治企图，发点牢骚，有人权自由。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"e217c3099f","type":"appellation","text":"要整，我就退团。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"f2285af2d9","type":"paragraph","text":"张存金(昆明工学院机械系学生)说：","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"d54a892f67","type":"subtitle","text":"中国现在是殖民地，比蒙古人统治还厉害","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"2ed1132562","type":"paragraph","text":"现在中国的统治是中国历史上从古未有的残酷统治。元人进入中国，十家有一个鞑子监视；现在每家每地都有监视。","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"f176fa855a","type":"paragraph","text":"有人提现在中国是卖国政府。我补充一句，是一边倒，从前是半殖民地半封建社会，现在变成殖民地了。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"9fd1997dc5","type":"subtitle","text":"国家政策是执行莫斯科的指示","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"c3ab022f7a","type":"paragraph","text":"专家是监视，每个角落都有，放个屁都是香的。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"66bdde8625","type":"paragraph","text":"国家政策是执行莫斯科的指示和意图，所谓帮助是给我们坏机器，外边涂层漆，要我们仿苏联1937年的枪弹图制造枪弹，使我们停留在1937年的水平，苏联贷款利息比那国都高，抗日胜利后运走了很多机器，使得解放后工业停滞。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"0a2fdf489d","type":"subtitle","text":"中国没有民主","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"20620da803","type":"paragraph","text":"中国民主少，可以说没有。共产党征求意见，但提意见就是反党、反社会主义，所以是残酷统治。民主就是人民管理中国，现在是党管理中国。说中国好只是词句美化。选举是强加于人。工农谈好只是加入共产党的人，广大工农被迫得不敢说话，否则有生命之优。","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"54e79d5f4a","type":"appellation","text":"我认为有提打倒共产党的自由，也有提拥护共产党的自由。","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"6e76991564","type":"paragraph","text":"你们谈话就以为自由了，你们只不过是应声筒，并不自由，站在这个地位应该感到耻辱。","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"4e21ca9de9","type":"subtitle","text":"我要建立自己的统治，建立自己的理论","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"4f6d003cad","type":"paragraph","text":"我要建立自己的统治，要统治中国。为达到这个目的，要 用革命手段。共产党给人微小利益以巩固自己的统治。共产党是工人阶级的政党，从何谈起？工人党员才百分之几？中央常委有几个是工人？只是美名而已！","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"9390b77784","type":"paragraph","text":"要建立自己的理论，要探讨用什么办法驳倒“阶级斗争”，现在顾正泉得出“利益”两个字代替阶级斗争。要发挥和承继这个观点。","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"9cce3c2d07","type":"paragraph","text":"马列主义向工人灌输是强加于人，不打自招。如何寻求真理，建立自己的理论，现尚未得出。真理我们要探讨的。","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"02ea63b465","type":"paragraph","text":"江天龙：","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"c24b85d5e2","type":"appellation","text":"致院长","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"2b34bb739b","type":"paragraph","text":"院长阁下，爵士们！贵族们！","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"33f3aa0eaf","type":"paragraph","text":"1、你们的成绩已为群众所标榜，你们的丰功伟绩已为百姓所称颂，下马观花吧！坐在王宫相府里。","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"904397cda7","type":"paragraph","text":"2、取消贵族的特权，取消阎王科（干部科）取消太太科（学生科）。","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"f54a2c4767","type":"paragraph","text":"3、精“兵”简政，撤免不称职的诸公，裁汰多余无用人员。","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"e52e070fe8","type":"paragraph","text":"4、惩办违法乱纪的权贵。","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"09c9f70a1d","type":"paragraph","text":"5、立即（奏）本皇上坚决改变我院之恶劣情景。","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"eba5c28e4e","type":"paragraph","text":"地一 庶民","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"27bcab7d27","type":"paragraph","text":"院长只求功名","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"63cd7c6d1c","type":"paragraph","text":"院长只求功名，","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"5e99c0e774","type":"paragraph","text":"百姓疾苦不过问，","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"75fe69e011","type":"paragraph","text":"可恨呀可恨！","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"74b75c17e7","type":"paragraph","text":"如何有此不平事？","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"f2c2337a6b","type":"paragraph","text":"因为他们是贵人！爵士！","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"4e408cdee6","type":"paragraph","text":"——高人一等。","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"a5339a14b2","type":"paragraph","text":"（注：以上二则录自工学院大字报，后一首诗为江天龙所写，标题是我们加的）","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"d7e94a8981","type":"paragraph","text":"吕瑾华(昆明工学院机械系学生)大字报：","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"3219db2fdb","type":"subtitle","text":"三大敌人内幕","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"b53b566dea","type":"paragraph","text":"官僚主义作后队，教条主义杀冲锋，宗派主义装子弹，它们在人们眼中晃晃然。欲摆脱形影，但人民的眼睛是雪亮的，不会受到他们的欺骗。","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"},{"id":"2dc922a096","type":"paragraph","text":"当官僚主义挨打时，教条主义自然会帮助它披着马列主义外衣来反抗人们，自然会用上很漂亮的词句，为官僚主义辩护。不问鸣者的动机，专在某些词句上强词夺理，否认一切，反对过火了变为敌我矛盾了！这时宗派主义抬着大刀，扛着阔斧，无情打击。反对三害中它们在作垂死的挣扎，勇敢的人们起来吧！我们宣誓要彻底反掉它！静静先生，请照镜子吧？","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59"}],"page":{"id":"9b3e471fab","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa529ded59","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}